{
  "texts": [
    "BERT can express tokenized words as corresponding word embeddings.",
    "BERT is better at handling unlabeled data and the word vector expressed by BERT includes context information in addition to its own information.",
    "We utilized a pretrained language mode, namely Turkish BERT (BERTurk) for this purpose.",
    "Deep learning models BILSTMRecurrent neural network (RNN) that can handle the vanishing gradient problem is known as Long Short-Term Memory (LSTM) network.",
    "LSTM is also better at maintaining long-range connections and understanding the connection between values at the start and end of a sequence."
  ]
}